{"tid":1501794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【終極大核彈！！！】【斷正】監控燈柱操作界面　中共監視香港大計　香港即將玩完 (2)","createTime":"2019-08-24T12:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T03:44:16.000Z","uid":69416,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"a3cd7a975ad3632a9d95bd88acf0fb3eafc33891","tid":1501794,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:56:25.000Z","msg":"前一篇：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1501454/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1501454/page/1</a><br />\n話說本人外國勢力 身邊有朋友手痕去用個死人網<br />\n<a href=\"https://ticktack.tech/loginApp.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fticktack.tech%2FloginApp.html&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=036d9489\" target=\"_blank\">https://ticktack.tech/loginApp.html</a><br />\n發現個網極容易入 ac pw直頭係同一個字<br />\n不單止有哂成個系統既操作版面<br />\n而且似乎仲顯示埋香港智能燈柱既位置 (下面地圖顯示既藍色方塊)<br />\n點知越睇越唔對路...點解明明有D係無智能燈柱都會有...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">本人大膽估計哩個地圖係中共將來打算安裝監視燈柱既分佈圖</span></strong></span><br />\n大家幫幫手推 真係好撚恐怖 如果成事香港必定玩完<br />\n想避燈柱直頭要避到上郊野公園<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中共真係打算將香港人清算 趕盡殺絕 滅族</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrsJe7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrsJe7d.jpg&h=077fac26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TuEGMdT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTuEGMdT.jpg&h=20d652c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEYwo0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEYwo0z.jpg&h=39c79727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kc4C30z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKc4C30z.jpg&h=20e6c870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZ34J0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u