乎仲顯示埋香港智能燈柱既位置 (下面地圖顯示既藍色方塊)<br />\n點知越睇越唔對路...點解明明有D係無智能燈柱都會有...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">本人大膽估計哩個地圖係中共將來打算安裝監視燈柱既分佈圖</span></strong></span><br />\n大家幫幫手推 真係好撚恐怖 如果成事香港必定玩完<br />\n想避燈柱直頭要避到上郊野公園<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中共真係打算將香港人清算 趕盡殺絕 滅族</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrsJe7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrsJe7d.jpg&h=077fac26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TuEGMdT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTuEGMdT.jpg&h=20d652c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEYwo0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEYwo0z.jpg&h=39c79727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kc4C30z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKc4C30z.jpg&h=20e6c870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZ34J0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZ34J0A.jpg&h=b13d7105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xLP3ZyV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxLP3ZyV.jpg&h=4733dfa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTB2vFB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTB2vFB.jpg&h=79abbcd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WZNJe7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZNJe7g.jpg&h=6ea86ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Je4GMdY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJe4GMdY.jpg&h=1d1245bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ibZvEyY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FibZvEyY.jpg&h=b7bbd0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n